    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Step into the Whimsical World Of Lefty!</h2>Welcome to Lefty, a cozy 3D puzzle game set in a colorful, whimsical, and strange world. Join Lefty, a unique left-handed character, on a journey to find the way home—one step at a time. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090820/extras/428b977feeaa49514ea7ba604a79fecf.poster.avif?t=1755755571\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090820/extras/428b977feeaa49514ea7ba604a79fecf.webm?t=1755755571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090820/extras/428b977feeaa49514ea7ba604a79fecf.mp4?t=1755755571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>But there’s a twist: in this world, Lefty can only move to the right!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Key Features</h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Culturally Inspired Gameplay</h2>Experience gameplay inspired by the Arabic cultural tradition of preferring to use the right hand in everyday life. Navigate through fun, satisfying puzzles that challenge your mind in delightful ways.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Unique Movement Mechanics</h2>Control Lefty as he moves exclusively to the right. Shift your perspective, rotating each level to the right, adding layers of complexity and strategy to each puzzle, and ensuring every move counts.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090820/extras/7db71120c7042182bbd4e90c8e0d288f.poster.avif?t=1755755571\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090820/extras/7db71120c7042182bbd4e90c8e0d288f.webm?t=1755755571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090820/extras/7db71120c7042182bbd4e90c8e0d288f.mp4?t=1755755571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Whimsical Art Style</h2>Immerse yourself in Lefty’s simple, whimsical, and colorful art style. Quirky otherworldly visuals that delight and disorient in equal measure!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Increasing Complexity</h2>Tackle mazes that become progressively more complex, featuring obstacles like moving walls, rising walls, moving goals, locked paths, and flipping mazes. Plan your path carefully to overcome each challenge.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090820/extras/40fd6d0af311f29e4a766280edad8593.poster.avif?t=1755755571\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090820/extras/40fd6d0af311f29e4a766280edad8593.webm?t=1755755571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3090820/extras/40fd6d0af311f29e4a766280edad8593.mp4?t=1755755571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Puzzle Variety</h2>Encounter a wide variety of puzzles that require active planning and quick thinking. Navigate through mazes with minimal rotations and master the unique mechanics of this right-turning world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Accessible Controls</h2>Enjoy super accessible and easy-to-use controls, whether you prefer a controller or mouse and keyboard. Lefty is designed to be approachable for all players.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Why You'll Love Lefty</h2>Lefty is perfect for fans of cozy games, puzzle games, and casual games. Its unique blend of cultural inspiration, whimsical art, and simply-yet-satisfying mechanics hopes to offer a charming experience. Whether you’re unwinding after a long day or seeking a stimulating challenge, Lefty will give you a delightful escape into a world where every turn matters.<br><br>So, what are you waiting for? Embark on Lefty's journey and see the world from a new perspective—one right turn at a time!",
